Query: SELECT * FROM sampled_aka_title_1 AS aka_t,    sampled_company_name_1 AS cn,    sampled_company_type_1 AS ct,    sampled_info_type_1 AS it1,    sampled_keyword_1 AS k,    sampled_movie_companies_1 AS mc,    sampled_movie_info_1 AS mi,    sampled_movie_keyword_1 AS mk,    sampled_title_1 AS t WHERE t.id = aka_t.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = aka_t.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = aka_t.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = aka_t.movie_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' AND it1.info = 'release dates' AND mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(theatrical)%' AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%' AND mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%' AND t.production_year > 1950 LIMIT 5;
